{"tid":1491590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【 818集會籌款數字公佈 】","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:11:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec99cd247dd98b3dd2e8aaab48b3c5b814367ba0","tid":1491590,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"基金公佈818集會及疏散路線上，各團體之籌款數字，合共為$8,082,592.40，在此感謝香港人、各政黨及團隊對反送中運動者，及本基金之支持。<br />\n<br />\n818當日協助基金籌款之政黨、團體名單（排名不分先後）︰民主黨、社會民主連線、工黨、人民力量、區政聯盟、荃民議政、民間人權陣線。<br />\n<br />\n另外，基金將於本周末，發佈第二期工作簡報，以便公眾監察。<br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金<br />\n2019年8月20日<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/68734352_1390490421104544_4100365905525997568_n.png?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQmO2wKZDBqzBGLyY13bXMh7-mmRqfcyhhvocYIt4D4_FnmKPcpknH5EmE7Fbn-OJL4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=1d9972be2780278b5eb3e6e7e90c05d1&amp;oe=5E109E29\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.15752-9%2F68734352_1390490421104544_4100365905525997568_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQmO2wKZDBqzBGLyY13bXMh7-mmRqfcyhhvocYIt4D4_FnmKPcpknH5EmE7Fbn-OJL4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D1d9972be2780278b5eb3e6e7e90c05d1%26oe%3D5E109E29&h=36c3656c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58035602acba91743cf667dae3ee007bf191c3c8","tid":1491590,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}